For loops:
You have a list and you need to use them
for var-name in {list}
do
	{Command}
done

$(seq 1 10) <- make a list of sequence from 1 to 10 numbers 
{1..10} <- same as above


While loops:
Execute code while an expresion is true

while [ condition ]
do
	{Command}
done

((counter++)) <- increment a counter aritmetic and evaluation at same time because it have double ((
